WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.410 --> 00:00:05.260
In a startup's life, there is no single
day that will not bring a new challenge.

00:00:05.260 --> 00:00:08.990
So what are sort of the common
challenges that students will face

00:00:08.990 --> 00:00:12.310
as they're on their path
to monetization nirvana?

00:00:12.310 --> 00:00:15.570
&gt;&gt; There are three main ones:
acquisition, retention, and earning.

00:00:15.570 --> 00:00:20.010
Acquisition, this is not an easy step.

00:00:20.010 --> 00:00:24.540
How can you put your product in front
of enough users so some of them, 4% or

00:00:24.540 --> 00:00:27.190
less, will convert and pay for it?

00:00:27.190 --> 00:00:31.790
In many cases, you should focus and
narrow this search.

00:00:31.790 --> 00:00:32.580
Less is more here.

00:00:33.670 --> 00:00:38.280
If you can focus on a niche segment in
the market, you will get a better chance

00:00:38.280 --> 00:00:42.160
to reach the users who
are willing to try your product.

00:00:42.160 --> 00:00:43.750
Second, exciting your audience.

00:00:43.750 --> 00:00:45.640
Surprise them with your quality.

00:00:45.640 --> 00:00:47.430
It's easy to say how to do.

00:00:47.430 --> 00:00:49.090
Nevertheless you want to do it.

00:00:49.090 --> 00:00:51.330
You wish to invest in their
attention of your users.

00:00:51.330 --> 00:00:54.730
And a known way to do it is by
creating wonderful experience.

00:00:54.730 --> 00:00:58.170
Users love quality and simplicity.

00:00:58.170 --> 00:01:03.410
Third, earning in commerce,
make it easy for them to pay.

00:01:03.410 --> 00:01:07.690
In mobile eCommerce there's lots
of forms with lots of fields.

00:01:07.690 --> 00:01:11.580
We go into more details on
how to reduce the friction

00:01:11.580 --> 00:01:14.137
in that process a bit later.

00:01:14.137 --> 00:01:20.022
In app purchases, charge the right users
with the right offer at the right time.

00:01:20.022 --> 00:01:24.440
There are many user segments and
each deserve its own customize offering.

00:01:24.440 --> 00:01:31.160
For example, in a mobile gaming app, 5%
of the users drove 95% of the revenue.

00:01:31.160 --> 00:01:35.844
So it was a smart move to improve
the offering for these 5%.

00:01:35.844 --> 00:01:40.840
Ads, Do your best to use ads that
enhance the user experience.

